name: Aquarium
description:
Aquarium, a voxel art piece based on one of my aquariums.


A little box that transports you into another world.

This aquarium is filled with stem plants, floating plants, wood, and stones. The water is filtered by a small sponge filter which keeps all the baby shrimp that clean the tank safe.

Size: 2048px x 1152px
File type: png
